{"tid":1827444,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[SCMP]歐盟前駐南韓大使涉嫌為中國國安部做間諜！！","createTime":"2020-01-17T03:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T04:29:29.000Z","uid":10200,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2481e01150dd0ffaf0f5ca2fb9cba609f1d7fbb8","tid":1827444,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3046484/eus-former-ambassador-south-korea-suspect-china-spy-probe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle%2F3046484%2Feus-former-ambassador-south-korea-suspect-china-spy-probe&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcygfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=d177dcec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3046484/eus-former-ambassador-south-korea-suspect-china-spy-probe</a><br />\n<br />\nSources name ex-diplomat after German authorities raid flats and offices as part of an investigation into an alleged link with China&rsquo;s top foreign intelligence unit."},{"pid":"0dd51d7e0533c8875f8975c24bd26f947da8c2ca","tid":1827444,"uid":10200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"擁有德國同匈牙利國籍嘅gerhard sabathil同另外兩個人嘅住宅同辦公室係星期三晚突然被德國機關上門調查<br />\n<br />\nSecurity sources said German authorities began an investigation last year after receiving information from the intelligence community. The investigators then listened to telephone calls and tracked three suspects&rsquo; travel records, according to German newspaper S&uuml;ddeutsche Zeitung.<br />\n<br />\nIts report, which did not name any suspects, said a German ex-diplomat provided the Chinese ministry with economic and private information. <span style=\"color: red;\">During a trip to China, the ex-diplomat appeared to have held meetings with a so-called executive officer of the Ministry of State Security, Zeitung said.</span>"},{"pid":"301ee740d35991c7240dd48036d4d78c46f8566f","tid":1827444,"uid":10200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"德國雜誌之前已經開始調查同埋披露咗有關人士嘅細節 但當時冇公報到嫌疑人嘅身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe work history of Sabathil, who was previously ambassador to Norway and Iceland and led the EU representative office in Germany, matches the details published by Germany&rsquo;s Der Spiegel magazine, which first reported on the investigation, without disclosing any names of suspects.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">應該係total9個人</span>被上門調查<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIn total, nine addresses were raided on Wednesday in Berlin, Brussels and the German states of Bavaria and Baden-W&uuml;rttemberg."},{"pid":"e48c3411776ac0c6d1160d0c9525d35512112a68","tid":1827444,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:21:49.000Z","msg":"Pusj"},{"pid":"a6df5af43c601fbd80178296c755b99a90c8bce8","tid":1827444,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:22:20.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個閪婆奶夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a53902705424b1f67571cbe8152088b78fce29","tid":1827444,"uid":133042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"54a40a5f820f4cbddfd18810fb7fa2d959938535","tid":1827444,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6df5af43c601fbd80178296c755b99a90c8bce8","tid":1827444,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03: