,"uid":34777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"54a40a5f820f4cbddfd18810fb7fa2d959938535","tid":1827444,"uid":37058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6df5af43c601fbd80178296c755b99a90c8bce8","tid":1827444,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:22:20.000Z","msg":"德國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個閪婆奶夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:30:15.000Z","msg":"個閪婆落台啦 奶共奶到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:31:22.000Z","msg":"都唔撚知係咪收咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n堂堂大國 追撚住支共條撚係咁含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:33:22.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀 <br />\n默克爾強調，孤立中國不是出路，又稱中國崛起是依靠勤奮及創意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826974\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826974</a>"},{"pid":"18b9f947f0046ee0361263e563df881c2bf877e0","tid":1827444,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:34:32.000Z","msg":"最大共碟咪個德國總理囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a289ba263018ef009a94b4965d066860e00d8d","tid":1827444,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"《明鏡周刊》報道稱，德國嘅前歐盟外交官與一家知名嘅德國遊說公司兩名員工涉嫌為中國從事間諜活動。<br />\n<br />\n其中兩人涉嫌向中國國家安全部提供私人同工作嘅信息。第三個人就僅表示有噉嘅意願。警方喺檢察院授權下，自清早起對柏林，布魯塞爾，巴登-符騰堡州和巴伐利亞州嘅9處地方搜查。所涉及嘅係嫌疑人嘅住所同辦公室。主要調查對象係歐盟委員會一名前工作人員，後就任歐盟對外事務部外交官。佢喺布魯塞爾期間就任領導職位，之後作為歐盟大使喺多個國家任職。2017年，佢結束喺歐盟嘅職業生涯，進入一家遊說公司做到而家。同年佢開始向中國情報人員提供信息。佢仲征召另外兩名被告加入。其中一人前往中國與嗰名可疑嘅中國情報人員進行咗會面。<br />\n<br />\n此案涉及嘅嗰間遊說公司過去曾為知名德國大企業提供諮詢。"},{"pid":"4951b8678aa069d44357093a4b9bff826bc339f8","tid":1827444,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6a289ba263018ef009a94b4965d066860e00d8d","tid":1827444,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"《明鏡周刊》報道稱，德國嘅前歐盟外交官與一家知名嘅德國遊說公司兩名員工涉嫌為中國從事間諜活動。<br />\n<br />\n其中兩人涉嫌向中國國家安全部提供私人同工作嘅信息。第三個人就僅表示有噉嘅意願。警方喺檢察院授權下，自清早起對柏林，布魯塞爾，巴登-符騰堡州和巴伐利亞州嘅9處地方搜查。所涉及嘅係嫌疑人嘅住所同辦公室。主要調查對象係歐盟委員會一名前工作人員，後就任歐盟對外事務部外交官。佢喺布魯塞爾期間就任領導職位，之後作為歐盟大使喺多個國家任職。2017年，佢結束喺歐盟嘅職業生涯，進入一家遊說公司做到而家。同年佢開始向中國情報人員提供信息。佢仲征召另外兩名被告加入。其中一人前往中國與嗰名可疑嘅中國情報人員進行咗會面。<br />\n<br />\n此案涉及嘅嗰間遊說公司過去曾為知名德國大企業提供諮詢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"A lobbyist hired by this former diplomat also acted as an informant for the Chinese, it is understood. A third suspect <span style=\"color: red;\">is alleged to have agreed to provide information in the future</span>, according to the Der Spiegel report.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488f1d7fe04f243bca6be6d8820d9212f795018b","tid":1827444,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"Washington Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>The investigation comes at a time of heightened European concern about expanding Chinese spy networks in Europe. European Union officials were reported to have received internal warnings about the proliferation of Russian and Chinese spies in the vicinity of its Brussels offices last year.<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9a8c320dab8aa2f23f529de2d153808cbf9c5863","tid":1827444,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}